{"id": "757032", "revid": "45203278", "url": "https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki?curid=757032", "title": "David Fumero", "text": "David Fumero is an American actor and former fashion model. Fumero is best known for his roles as Cristian Vega on \"One Life to Live\", Mike Sandoval on \"Power\", and as the man who swept Mariah Carey off her feet on the beach in her video for her song \"Honey\".\nPersonal life.\nDavid Fumero was born on December 29, 1972, in Havana, Cuba. He is a former United States Marine.\nOn December 9, 2007, Fumero married his \"One Life to Live\" co-star Melissa Fumero (n\u00e9e Gallo) who played Adriana Cramer on the show. They have two children together, a son born in March 2016 and another son born in February 2020."}
